      "createdAt": "2020-09-16T16:16:12Z",
      "reactions": 14,
      "body": "My decision is using [flat](https://www.npmjs.com/package/flat) library:\r\n```javascript\r\nimport flat from 'flat';\r\n\r\nconst data = [{ foo: { bar: 'Bar' } }];\r\nconst workbook = new Excel.Workbook();\r\nconst worksheet = workbook.addWorksheet('FooBar');\r\n\r\nworksheet.columns = [{ header: 'Foo', key: 'foo.bar' }];\r\nworksheet.addRows(data.map(row => flat(row))); // [{ foo: { bar: 'Bar' } }] --> [{ 'foo.bar': 'Bar' } }]\r\n```"
